&lt;p&gt;Databricks is looking for a bold, strategic, and execution-oriented senior executive to lead our Manufacturing industry go-to-market (GTM) motion across Asia Pacific and Japan (APJ). As a key member of our global industry GTM team, you will shape and drive how Databricks engages the industrial sectors in one of the world&#39;s most dynamic and complex regional markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to the Global GTM Head for Manufacturing, Transportation, and Energy, with deep day-to-day collaboration with APJ sales, field engineering, and GTM leadership. You will operate at the intersection of industry expertise, customer engagement, and commercial strategy - helping Databricks win in a market where data and AI are redefining how physical products are built, delivered, and optimized.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you bring deep industry domain knowledge, a bias for action, and a proven track record of harnessing the transformative potential of data and AI to drive real business value - we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the strategic and operational execution of GTM initiatives across the manufacturing and automotive industries in APJ, driving pipeline growth and accelerating customer adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong alignment with APJ sales, field engineering, marketing, partnerships, and product teams to develop and execute industry-specific GTM programs that convert market opportunity into revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate and maintain executive-level relationships with customers, partners, and key industry stakeholders across the APJ region — with particular focus on Japan, Korea, and India&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver thought leadership through industry publications, conferences, and executive briefings to position Databricks as the platform of choice for the industry&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide ongoing analysis of market trends, competitive dynamics, and customer needs to sharpen our industry strategy and identify high-value growth opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define, track, and report on key performance indicators (KPIs) for GTM initiatives, continuously refining plans based on data and field insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel regularly across the APJ region to support customer meetings, executive engagements, and industry events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
