&lt;li&gt;10+ years of leadership experience in the manufacturing sector, including at least 5 years in a GTM, strategy, or business development role within enterprise technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success taking technology products or platforms to market with a clear industry focus and measurable commercial outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert-level domain knowledge in one or more of the following areas: software-defined vehicles, industrial AI, agentic supply chain management, or AI-driven engineering and R&amp;amp;D&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with key manufacturing and automotive industry standards bodies and frameworks across the APJ region&lt;/li&gt;
