&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to influence and lead cross-functional teams without direct authority in a matrixed, fast-moving organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of building trusted relationships with senior executives in a multilingual, multicultural market like APJ&lt;/li&gt;
